---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Tim Raysby">
  <section class="grid md:grid-cols-[200px_1fr] gap-10 items-start">
    <img
      src="/headshot.png"
      alt="Tim Raysby"
      width="200"
      height="200"
      class="w-full md:w-48 h-auto border border-charcoal-lighter"
    />

    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-green mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="w-8 h-px bg-green"></span>
        About
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Intent-driven engineer.<br/>
        <em>AI orchestrator.</em><br/>
        Problem solver.
      </h1>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-ink-dim text-sm font-mono max-w-prose">
        <p>I build agentic AI systems and ship production code where ownership meets velocity.</p>

        <p>Most of the AI economy is a tax on attention — every prompt, every memory, every artifact you produce billed by the token, owned by someone else. There is a different way: infrastructure that runs on the machine in front of you.</p>

        <p>By day I am a senior engineer at a major insurer. Evenings and weekends I build NEXUS, my personal AI infrastructure. This site, every essay, every product — produced on it.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-12 font-mono text-xs text-green tracking-widest uppercase">
        build &middot; orchestrate &middot; solve
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
